---
import Layout from "../layouts/index.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div
    class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert prose-p:indent-4 prose-p:text-base md:prose-p:text-lg lg:prose-p:text-xl xl:prose-p:text-2xl text-justify font-extralight text-balance hyphens-manual md:my-12"
  >
    <h1
      class="text-left text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
    >
      Meet me, Yusoof Moh
    </h1>

    <p>
      In the name of Allah—by His grace. I’m Yusoof (<i>yoo-soof</i>), based in
      Malang and collaborating remotely across Indonesia. I’m a full-stack
      engineer focused on TypeScript/React (TanStack), Node/Bun, Hono, and solid
      DevOps with Docker, Traefik, and CI/CD. I also work on mobile with React
      Native/Capacitor and keep observability sharp (Sentry, SigNoz).
    </p>

    <p>
      Beyond code, I cultivate edamame, enjoy regional motorcycle tours, and
      keep a steady habit of deep research and learning.
    </p>

    <p>
      My understanding of Islam follows the way of the first three generations
      of the Ummah, focusing on <i>tawhid</i> and <i>tafsir</i>. I teach private
      <i>tahsin</i> and support local Muslim communities—hoping to contribute, even
      in small ways, to the da'wah.
    </p>

    <p>
      Recently, I’ve been building practical tools for Indonesian SMEs,
      standardizing CI/CD across monorepos, and shipping a <strong
        >multi-tenant booking & operations platform</strong
      > for service businesses (web + mobile)—from schema and APIs to deployments
      on Docker Swarm with full observability. I’m open to meaningful remote/contract
      collaborations. Reach me via
      <a
        class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
        href="mailto:me@yusoofsh.id"
        onclick="sa_event('email_clicked')"
        rel="noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        aria-label="Email Yusoof">Mail</a
      >
      /
      <a
        class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
        href="/twitter"
        onclick="sa_event('twitter_clicked')"
        rel="noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        aria-label="Yusoof on Twitter">Twitter</a
      >
      /
      <a
        class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
        href="/linkedin"
        onclick="sa_event('linkedin_clicked')"
        rel="noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        aria-label="Yusoof on LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a
      >
      /
      <a
        class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
        href="/github"
        onclick="sa_event('github_clicked')"
        rel="noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        aria-label="Yusoof on GitHub">GitHub</a
      >. May Allah bless our efforts and guide us to His everlasting mercy.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
